ActCanadian Environmental Protection Act, 1999
Department of Fisheries and Oceans Act
SubjectCanada-Ontario Agreement on Great Lakes Water Quality and Ecosystem Health, 2021
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of the Environment and the Minister of Fisheries and Oceans to ENTER INTO a CANADA-ONTARIO AGREEMENT ON GREAT LAKES WATER QUALITY AND ECOSYSTEM HEALTH, 2021 with the Government of Ontario, which will become effective upon signature and remain in force for five years following the date on which the Agreement is signed.
